sentences: Laura Elizabeth Arabosa Izibor (born 13 May 1987) is an Irish recording artist, musician and producer.
She went on to win an award at the 2006 Meteor Music Awards.
She also performed at that year's Electric Picnic music festival and Music Ireland 2007.
Her debut album, Let the Truth Be Told, was released in Ireland on 8 May 2009.
